channel.title: Rainbow - 700 Customs
channel.description:
I'm pretty much done with Rainbow; have fun with our models. You don't have to give credits, but if you see these guys:
Mikegau44 Racecar Supernova Im Hunter Ilixoxili HyphyMike Salthesexy Oh-Noes Fyrus Blane
give them a big thanks if you will use them in any way. Notice that only around a quarter of our non-recolored models are actually original (by our own modeling team); I mostly "borrowed" the rest from various servers, such as CheatSkape, FreeRoam, BainScape, and MikeScape.
Download: [url=http://skyrealm.net/downloads/pr_models.zip]http://skyrealm.net/downloads/pr_models.zip[/url]
Obviously they won't be "compatible" with your own base; do the work yourself and refactor whatever variables you need to refactor. I assume that if you use this, you have a brain.
Have fun and enjoy.
